Subdomain (DDD)	Break big â€œGodâ€ parts by logical domain	Subdomain, Bounded Context, DDD

ğŸ§  Why Does This Matter (Why Use These Patterns)?
Makes large systems easier to scale, test, and deploy independently 


Helps avoid complex tangled code (God Classes) that try to do everything.

Teams can work on separate parts without stepping on each otherâ€™s toes. 
